transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Jimmy. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hey, man, how are you? I'm doing good. How are you doing?

Speaker 1: Good. I just received the order and—

Speaker 2: It just came out traditional sedentist health. I wanted to try the AGV.

Speaker 1: Okay. All right.

Speaker 2: I have your information pulled up here. Is this Gordon I'm speaking to?

Speaker 1: Yes, it is.

Speaker 2: Hey Gordon, let me ask, did you order online when you placed your order?

Speaker 1: I did.

Speaker 2: Okay, I don't know why—

Speaker 1: Some sedentist has been, every now and then there's a little confusion on the order when it's done online.

Speaker 2: But I'm going to take care of you, Gordon.

Speaker 1: I'm going to get you, you look like you got 20 of them because you ordered 10 and you got the extra 10 as well.

Speaker 2: So I'm going to send you out 20 of the AGV Viagras, of course, no charges. You should have got that at first.

Speaker 1: I'm gonna take care of that for you today.

Speaker 2: Let me just briefly explain to you how the pills are going to look compared to what you received.

Speaker 1: They're still going to be a white shaped diamond pill, but they're going to have the number 100 on the back.

Speaker 2: That's how you're going to know that it's the AGV.

Speaker 1: Okay, and I'm going to get those sent out to you today. Don't worry about the ones you got.

Speaker 2: Those are still good Viagras you got, but it's not the AGV.

Speaker 1: So don't worry about trying to return those, but I'm going to get you out those 20 to you today. Okay?

Speaker 2: All right. Thank you.

Speaker 1: And I'll give it to you.

Speaker 2: I'm confirming it. 1-810 Grandberry Way, right? Frederick Rowland?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 2: All right. I got you covered, Gordon. No problem.

Speaker 1: All right, man. Thank you.

Speaker 2: Sure. Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye.
